verbose_text: Analysis of cyclin D1 and bax expression in HCAEC treated with recombinant TF (2 U/mL) and purified fVIIa (0-10 nM) indicated entry into the cell cycle regardless of fVIIa concentration, in agreement with our previous findings, XREF_BIBR but was highest at 10 nM (XREF_FIG), while bax expression was only detectable at lower fVIIa concentrations (XREF_FIG).
